  "prompt": "Is Season 4 of Sherlock the last season in the series?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, Season 4 of \"Sherlock,\" which aired in early 2017, is indeed the most recent season. There has been no official confirmation of a fifth season, and both co-creators, Steven Moffat and Mark Gatiss, along with Benedict Cumberbatch and Martin Freeman, have suggested that they may not return for more episodes. However, there have also been hints that they are open to revisiting the series in the future. For the latest information on any potential new seasons, it's best to check official announcements or recent news updates.",
